<div class="col-md-12 col-md-offset-1">
<h3 class="font-32"><strong> Objectives of Chaanan are:</strong></h3>
<p class="font-24 margin-vertical-20 font-italic" style="text-align:justify;">1.&nbsp&nbspProvide vocational training and employment opportunities to persons with intellectual disability. </p>
<p class="font-24 margin-vertical-20 font-italic" style="text-align:justify;">2.&nbsp&nbspEmpower the parents by organizing training workshops, conferences, lectures, counseling services and various events etc </p>
<p class="font-24 margin-vertical-20 font-italic" style="text-align:justify;">3.&nbsp&nbspProvide dignified life to PwIDDs. </p>
<p class="font-24 margin-vertical-20 font-italic" style="text-align:justify;">4.&nbsp&nbspMake society aware and sensitize the society for Inclusion . </p>
<p class="font-24 margin-vertical-20 font-italic" style="text-align:justify;">5.&nbsp&nbspTo be the voice of PwIDDs and their parents by raising their issues and advocacy for their rights with Government. </p>
</div>
